  "texts": [
    "But does the LLM itself remain stuck in a vicious circle no matter how big its database is?",
    "or can some of the biases we discussed help it break out?",
    "(I think not; I think that the biases can only increase the constraints on what the LLM says, and that this may help explain how come LLMs can do so unexpectedly well despite that teacher/learner asymmetry.)",
    "--Please reply critically, not with compliance and compliments.",
    "The Recursive Nature of Dictionary Definitions: As you rightly pointed out, dictionary definitions represent a form of IVG."
